name: 超级兔子人
description:
Super Rabbit Man is a super-magic click-decision game.

Help Super Rabbit Man hug the beloved radish to return to the moon!

- The rules are simple, easy to use, easy to click to spray, pick radish can increase the number of spray!
- Provide more than 5 characters, the greater the ability of the character!
- Various props can improve the jetting ability.
